Cinder is an independent, greenfield Minecraft shaderpack-loader project.
The Iris Shaders project was consulted as a public behavioral reference for
legacy shaderpack concepts. Cinder is not a fork of Iris, includes no Iris
source code, assets, strings, test fixtures, or Git history, and is not
affiliated with or endorsed by the Iris Project.

Iris Shaders: https://github.com/IrisShaders/Iris
